data.description: Stunning River Oaks home located in the Mandeville School District with 4 bedrooms, 2 baths with a separate 13x15 office. This home boast high ceilings, wood and tiled floors, gourmet kitchen with granite counters and tiled backsplash, wall of windows, oversized master suite wiht walk in shower and tub. Enjoy the community pool and tennis courts.
